# Main page title;Lightbeam for Firefox
Lightbeam richin Firefox


;Lightbeam is a Firefox add-on that uses interactive visualizations to show you the first and third party sites you interact with on the Web.
Lightbeam jun rutz'aqat Firefox, ri nrokisaj silonel taq tz'etoj, nuk'üt chawäch ri nimaläj taq ruxaq k'amaya'l chuqa' ri ta ruxaq k'amaya'l kichin aj rox winaqi', achoq kik'in yatzijon pa Ajk'amaya'l.


;Shine a Light on Who’s Watching You
Ke'atzu' ri yetzeto awichin


;See who’s tracking you online
Tawetamaj achike yatz'eto pa k'amab'ey.


;As you browse, Lightbeam reveals the full depth of the Web today, including parts that are not transparent to the average user.
Toq atokinäq pa k'amaya'l, Lightbeam nuk'üt pe ri tz'aqät runimilem Ajk'amaya'l wakami, nitz'aqatisäx taq ruch'akul ri man e saqsöj ta chuwäch ri loman winäq.


