;How Lightbeam Works
Achike rub'eyal nisamäj Lightbeam


;Download and run the Lightbeam add-on in your Firefox browser.
Taqasaj chuqa' tatzija' ri Lightbeam tz'aqat pa ri Firefox akanob'al.


;Lightbeam will create a record of events for every site you visit and every third party site that is stored locally on your browser.
Lightbeam xtunük' jun kitz'ib'axik taq molojri'ïl chi kijujunal ri taq ruxaq k'amaya'l xke'atz'ët chuqa' chi kijujunal ri ruxaq kik'amaya'l aj rox ri xke'uxqanëx pa ri akanob'al:


;Lightbeam visually graphs these events to highlight the interactions between sites you intentionally visit and the third parties.
Lightbeam nuwachib'ej kitz'etik re taq molojri'ïl re', richin nuya' ketal ri taq tzijonem chi kikojol ri taq ruxaq k'amaya'l junelïk e'atz'eton chuqa' ri taq ruxaq kik'amaya'l aj rox.


;Lightbeam will continue to add to your graph as you browse the Web. You can stop Lightbeam at any time by disabling it or uninstalling the add-on. Your Lightbeam data can be easily saved or deleted.
Ligthbeam junelïk xkerutz'aqatisaj taq wachib'äl toq xkatokiyaj pa Ajk'amaya'l. Pa xab'achike ramaj yatikïr nachüp ri Lightbeam, rik'in ruchupuk o relesaxik ri tz'aqat. Ri taq atzij pa Lightbeam tikirel yeyak o yeyuj el pan aninäq.


;Tracking & privacy
Kanoxïk & ichinanem


;Not all tracking is bad. Many services rely on user data to provide relevant content and enhance your online experience.
Man konojel ta ri taq kanoxïk man e ütz ta. K'ïy taq samaj nikikuqub'a' kik'u'x chi rij ri etamab'äl naya' chi ke richin nikutzilaj ri awetamab'al pa k'amab'ey.


;But tracking can happen without the user’s knowledge.
Xa xe chi ri kanoxïk nitikïr nik'ulwachitäj, akuchi' majun retaman ri winäq.


;That’s not okay for some.
Chi kiwäch jujun, ri ri' man ütz ta.


;It should be you who decides when, how and if you want your browsing data to be shared. We recognize the importance of transparency and our mission is all about empowering users — both with tools and information.
K'o ta chi ja rat ri yana'ojin jampe', achike rub'eyal chuqa' we nawajo' nakomonij ri awetamab'al pa ruwi' okem pa k'amaya'l. Röj niqaya' rejqalem ri ch'ajch'öj samaj chuqa' ri taqel qataqanem nuch'ojij chi tiya' kuchuqa' ri winaqi' — rik'in taq samajib'äl achi'el chuqa' rik'in taq etamab'äl.


;Explore the database
Takanoj ri rucholxe'el tzij


;In the Lightbeam database, you will be able to browse first and third-party connection data uploaded by donors who use the Lightbeam add-on.
Pa ri rucholxe'el tzij Lightbeam, xkatikïr ke'akanoj nimaläj chuqa' aj rox okem taq tzij ejotob'an kuma ri to'onela', ri ye'okisan ri Lightbeam tz'aqat.


;We’re building this crowd-sourced directory to encourage users to visualize the state of tracking as an aggregate and to examine relationships that exist on the Web.
Tajin niqanük' re cholb'äl re' rik'in jalajöj taq xe'el, richin niqayäk kik'u'x ri winaqi' chi nikitz'ët ri rub'anikil kanoxïk, achi'el jun rutz'aqat chuqa' richin yenik'öx ri taq tzijonem e k'o pa Ajk'amaya'l.


;Visualize your data
Tatz'eta' ri awetamab'al


;After you download and install the Lightbeam add-on to Firefox, it will begin to create a real time visualization of the websites you visit and all the third parties that are also active on those pages.
Chi rij naqasaj chuqa' nayäk ri Lightbeam tz'aqat richin Firefox, re re' xtutikirisaj yeruk'üt pe pa ri ramaj ri taq ruxaq k'amaya'l xke'atz'ët chuqa' konojel ri aj rox yetz'eto re taq ruxaq re'.


;Analyze your connections
Ke'anik'oj ri taq awokem pa k'amaya'l


;As your visualizations grow, you can take a closer look into the relationships between the various first and third party sites that are stored in your data. You can also reset or save your data at any time.
Toq yek'iyïr ri taq atz'etoj, yatikïr nachäp rutz'etik naqaj ri kikojol ri taq nimaläj chuqa' aj rox taq ruxaq k'amaya'l, ri e'uxqanen chi kikojol ri taq atzij. Chuqa' yatikïr natikirisaj chuqa' nayäk ri awetamab'al pa xab'achike ramaj.


;Contribute your data
Kato'on rik'in ri awetamab'al


;As a part of Lightbeam, we are creating a big-picture view of Internet tracking and of how first and third party sites are connected.
Achi'el ruch'akulal Lightbeam, tajin niqanük' jun chijun rutz'etoj kanoxïk pa k'amaya'l chuqa' achike rub'eyal eximon ri taq nimaläj chuqa' aj rox taq ruxaq k'amaya'l.


;To help us, you can contribute your data to our Lightbeam database.
Richin yojato, yatikïr yato'on rik'in ri taq awetamab'al richin ri rucholxe'el rutzij ri Lightbeam.


;Supported by the Ford Foundation
To'on ruma ri Ford Moloj


;The work at the Ford Foundation focuses on building outreach campaigns to help people understand online data tracking — both the benefits and the issues
Ri rusamaj ri Ford Moloj, nuya' retal chi kinuk'ik taq rutzijol richin yeruto' ri winaqi' chi niq'ax pa kiwi' chi rij ri kikanoxik taq tzij pa k'amab'ey achib'ilan apo kik'in ri taq rutzil — chuqa' ri taq ruk'ayewal


