# About page;About Lightbeam
Chi rij ri Lightbeam


;Lightbeam visualizes the relationships between the sites you visit and the third party sites that are active on those pages.
Ligthbeam yeruk'üt ri taq ximoj chi kikojol ri taq ruxaq k'amaya'l xke'atz'ët chuqa' ri taq aj rox ruxaq k'amaya'l, ri e tzijïl pa ri ruxaq ri'.


;How the add-on works
Achike rub'eyal nisamäj ri tz'aqat.


