Richin nasik'ij ch'aqa' chik pa ruwi' ri to'ïk, tatz'eta' <a href="{url}">{url}</a>


;Policy and the larger tracking narrative
Na'ojil chuqa' ri ruch'owik ri junelïk rojqaxik


;At Mozilla, we believe that everyone should have the tools to make their own decisions about their online privacy and who collects data on them.
Pa Mozilla, niqana'ojij chi konojel k'o chi nik'oje' ri taq samajib'äl kik'in richin yeq'ijun chi rij ri kichinaxik pa k'amab'ey chuqa' ri nimolo' richin ri retamab'al.


;With the Lightbeam add-on, we are providing a valuable (and open) community research platform that aims to raise awareness, promote analysis and, ultimately, affect policy change in the areas of tracking and privacy.
Rik'in ri Lightbeam tz'aqat chuqa' ri ruk'u'x rusamaj rucholxe'el taq tzij, niqaya' apo jun utziläj (chuqa' jamäl) temeb'äl pa ruwi' rujikilib'anem tinamït, ri nuya' ruq'ij chi tinimär ri na'oj, nitikirisäx ri ch'ob'oj, pa ruk'isib'äl kerusamajij ri taq rujaloj na'ojil pa ruk'ojlib'al kanoxïk chuqa' ichinanem.


;Lightbeam is one step in a larger, concerted effort by Mozilla and its partners to provide Web users with greater control and transparency of their personal data.
Lightbeam jun nimaläj samaj, jun uchuq'a' nuk'un ruma ri Mozilla chuqa' ri eruto'onela' richin nikiya' chi ke ri ruwinaq Ajk'amaya'l rik'in jun nïm chajinïk chuqa' ch'ajch'öj rusamajixik ri ichinan etamab'äl.


;Learn more about online tracking and privacy
Tasik'ij ch'aqa' chik pa ruwi' ri online kanoxïk chuqa' ichinanem


;The <a href="%s">Mozilla Foundation</a> is a non-profit organization that promotes the values of an open Web to the broader world. The larger Mozilla community sees the growing relevance of online privacy and is supporting several initiatives that tackle the issue in various ways.
Ri <a href="%s">Mozilla Moloj</a> jun moloj man rutzeqelib'en ta ch'akoj, ri yerutikirsaj taq rejqalem ri jaqäl k'amaya'l chijun ri ruwach'ulew. Ri nimaläj rutinamital Mozilla nuya' retal chi tajin nik'iyirisäx rejqalem ri ichinanem pa k'amab'ey chuqa' yeruto' cha'el taq na'oj, ri nikisamajij ri na'oj ri' pa jalajöj rub'anikil.


